quran[25]{c,v,t}:
  37,52,"Wi'anaynooЙ—o lam, e hoore yeddugol jalkita: kere an wonndiiЙ—o, hiЙ—a jeyaa e goongimЙ“e immintineede maayЙ“e Й“en?"
  37,53,"Eyoo si en maayii, en wontii mbulmbulndi e Жҙi'e kiЙ—Й—e, haray ko en immintinoyteeЙ“e yoЙ“itee njoЙ“di golle men Й—en aduna?"
  37,54,"WondinooЙ—o makko gomЙ—imЙ“e on, wi'ana wonndiiЙ“e mun Й“en ka Aljanna: on Жҙeewiday e am, anndugol battane wonndinooЙ—o lam yeddunooЙ—o ummital on?"
  37,55,"Kanko o Жҙeewa, o haynoo wondinooЙ—o makko on, ka tummbere Dulbunge."
  37,56,"o wi'a: mi woondirii Alla ! An oo wondinooЙ—o lam, a eЙ“Й“uno halkitirgol fii am, naatugol Yiite, sabu ko noodiraynoЙ—aa lam e keeferaaku, yedda fii ummital."
  37,57,"Si wanaa moЖҙЖҙere Alla nden e am, woni sabu mi feewiri gomЙ—inal, mi tawdeteno e lepteteeЙ“e Й“en, wano maa."
  37,58,"Wonaa non enen yimЙ“e Aljanna Й“en, en maayataa."
  37,59,"En maayataa, si wanaa maayde men aranere nden aduna. Wurin ko en duumotooЙ“e ka Aljanna, en wonaali kadi lepteteeЙ“e, wano yedduЙ“e Й“en huuwirtee."
  37,60,"Pellet, ko ndii njoЙ“di ndi Joomi men warjori en naatugol duumoo Aljanna, daЙ—a Yiite Й—oo, woni maloore mawnunde nden, nde yeru mun alaa."
  37,61,"Ko fii sugu ndii njoЙ“di mawndi Й—oo, woni ko waЙ—Й—ii nde gollooЙ“e gollanta. Tawde ko ndii woni ngeyngu tonatoongu."
  37,62,"Hara ko on neema mo Alla marani jeyaaЙ“e Makko laЙ“Й“inan Й“e Mo dawal Й“en, Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude jipporde e teddungal, kaa ko leggal "Zaqquumi" huЙ—aangal ka Alqur'aana ngal? Tawngal ko Гұaametee heeferЙ“e Й“en, ngal fayintaa ngal duncataa e ittugol heege!"
  37,63,"Men waЙ—ii ngal leggal, jarrabuyee, wonannde tooГұirЙ“e geddi e keeferaaku Й“en. Tawde Й“e wi'uno: Yiite Гұaamay leЙ—Й—e, Й—um holli, leggal fuЙ—ataa ka Yiite."
  37,64,"Laggal zaqquumi ngal, ko yaltirayngal ka kaaniri: ko ka tummbere Dulbunge, ngal yaltirta."
  37,65,"DimЙ—e ngal leggal, hino kaaniri nannditi wa ko'e seytanuuji. Si hunnde non kaanii, ko Й—um woni nde kaanii kadi kabaaru; Й—um holli, Гұaametee maggal on, ko ko Гұiddi."
  37,66,"KamЙ“e heeferЙ“e Й“en, pellet, ko e dimЙ—e ngal leggal haaЙ—ungal, woni ko Й“e dekkirta, Й“e hebbinira deedi maЙ“Й“e heegaaЙ—i."
  37,67,"Refti hino woodani e caggal nyaamgol leggal ngal, njaram, jillaaЙ—am, fatinaaЙ—am haa Гұiddi."
  37,68,"Refti ruttorde maЙ“Й“e nden, ko ka lepte DulЙ“oowe: Й“e iwa e lepte, Й“e yaha e lepte."
  37,69,"ЖҒee heeferЙ“e, Й“e tawu baabiraaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en, majjunooЙ“e laawol peewal ngol; Й“e jokkitii Й—on, ko aldaa e hujja."
  37,70,"ЖҒe woni e yaccagol jokka batteeji majjere baabiraaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en ko yaawi."
  37,71,"GomЙ—ii ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—de e aramЙ“e Й“en, majjiino, ado maЙ“Й“e. Wanaa yimЙ“e maa Й“en, an NulaaЙ—o, adii majjude e mofte Й—en."
  37,72,"GomЙ—ii le, Men nunulo e Й—en mofte adinooЙ“e, NulaaЙ“e, ko jertina e lepte Alla Й—en, kono Й“e yeddi."
  37,73,"Ndaaru an NulaaЙ—o, ko honno baЙ—tane Й“en jertinanooЙ“e salii, no wa'unoo! Ko Yitte Й“e sakkitori naatude, luttirooЙ“e ton, sabu salaare e fennugol Й“e NulaaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en."
  37,74,"Si wanaa jeyaaЙ“e Alla, laЙ“Й“inaaЙ“e Й“en; ko Й“en Й—on daЙ—oyta lepte Й—en Й—e Й“eya heeferЙ“e yeddunoo waЙ—tiniroya."
  37,75,"GomЙ—ii Nuuhu nodduno Men (yo o his) fewndo yimЙ“e makko Й“en fennunoo mo, e hoore ko o noddi Й“e e mun kon, iskin ko Men woni moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e noototooЙ“e. Tawde Men yaccinno toraare makko nden e maЙ“Й“e."
  37,76,"Men daЙ—ndi mo, kanko e Й“eynguure makko nden, wondude e gomЙ—imЙ“e mo Й“en, lorra yimЙ“e makko, e yoolagol tuufaan ngol, nelangol ngol e yimЙ“e makko yeddunooЙ“e Й“en."